    <briefdescription>
<para>Base class providing runtime type identification and safe casting. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>All endstone types that support runtime type narrowing (e.g., <ref refid="classendstone_1_1Permissible" kindref="compound">Permissible</ref>, <ref refid="classendstone_1_1ItemMeta" kindref="compound">ItemMeta</ref>) inherit from <ref refid="classendstone_1_1Object" kindref="compound">Object</ref>. Subclasses implement getClassTypeId() and isInstanceOf(), and the type hierarchy is registered with entt::meta at startup. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
